title: Your Pie
typeOfFood: Lacto, Pizza, Italian, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Franchise pizzeria. Choose your dough, toppings, and sauce. Has tofu alongside standard vegetable toppings, plus soy cheese (ask if vegan). A sorbet is dairy-free. Also serves paninis, salads and gelato and a few local craft beers are on tap. Gluten free crust available, plus gluten free pies are prepared separately.
